00:26:04,075 --> 00:26:05,405
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati-hati.</font>

381
00:26:21,426 --> 00:26:23,825
<font color=#FFFF00>JO HANG JOON</font>

382
00:26:29,666 --> 00:26:31,996
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hei, kau menangis?</i></font>

383
00:26:31,996 --> 00:26:33,436
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

384
00:26:35,065 --> 00:26:36,835
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa kali harus kuberitahu?</font>

385
00:26:37,635 --> 00:26:39,905
<font color=#FFFF00>Mataku kering.</font>

386
00:26:48,615 --> 00:26:51,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Akhirnya aku berhasil, Hang Joon Hyung.</font>

387
00:26:52,355 --> 00:26:53,716
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dong Tak.</i></font>

388
00:26:54,286 --> 00:26:56,855
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sekarang, kau pasti akan hidup
dengan baik tanpa aku.</i></font>

389
00:26:57,825 --> 00:27:01,226
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kerja bagus, Detektif Cha Dong Tak.</i></font>

390
00:27:31,456 --> 00:27:33,395
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah lama aku tidak menatap langit.</font>

391
00:27:51,645 --> 00:27:52,946
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau punya pemantik?</font>

392
00:27:53,916 --> 00:27:55,916
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sepertinya Detektif.</font>

393
00:27:55,916 --> 00:27:57,756
<font color=#FFFF00>Sangat tidak sopan meminta pemantik padaku.</font>

394
00:27:59,016 --> 00:28:01,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, aku sangat muak
dengan pemantik sialan itu.</font>

395
00:28:01,555 --> 00:28:03,456
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terus bersikap kasar
kepada yang lebih tua.</font>

396
00:28:07,325 --> 00:28:08,526
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang lebih tua?</font>

397
00:28:09,926 --> 00:28:12,536
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bertanya pada Detektif Jo
di depan abunya,</font>

398
00:28:13,295 --> 00:28:14,966
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan dia menyuruh kita berteman.</font>

399
00:28:15,305 --> 00:28:18,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau bersikeras lebih tua dariku
atau semacamnya,</font>

400
00:28:18,276 --> 00:28:19,436
<font color=#FFFF00>...itu akan sulit.</font>

401
00:28:19,436 --> 00:28:22,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa Detektif berteman
dengan penjahat?</font>

402
00:28:25,315 --> 00:28:26,746
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, kita berteman.</font>

403
00:28:29,545 --> 00:28:30,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau bercanda...</font>

404
00:28:30,885 --> 00:28:33,655
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan bilang tidak ingat,
aku akan membunuhmu.</font>

405
00:28:33,655 --> 00:28:34,756
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

406
00:28:35,956 --> 00:28:37,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan terus bercanda.</font>

407
00:28:37,825 --> 00:28:39,526
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu lah diriku.</font>

408
00:28:39,526 --> 00:28:41,466
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya ingin menjadi diriku.</font>

409
00:28:50,805 --> 00:28:53,835
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?/ Menurutmu? Ini borgol.</font>

410
00:28:54,545 --> 00:28:56,476
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuncinya ada di kantor.</font>

411
00:28:59,446 --> 00:29:00,476
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

412
00:29:01,315 --> 00:29:03,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang akan kau lakukan
mulai sekarang?</font>

413
00:29:03,815 --> 00:29:04,956
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah.</font>

414
00:29:06,186 --> 00:29:07,456
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin...</font>

415
00:29:07,885 --> 00:29:09,855
<font color=#FFFF00>...terus melakukan apa yang kubisa.</font>

416
00:29:09,855 --> 00:29:10,895
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

417
00:29:11,595 --> 00:29:12,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Menjadi penjahat?</font>

418
00:29:14,825 --> 00:29:15,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

419
00:29:16,526 --> 00:29:19,536
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan tetap di sisimu...</font>

420
00:29:19,536 --> 00:29:22,605
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, pesuruh./ Pesuruh?</font>

421
00:29:23,006 --> 00:29:26,135
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak percaya kau menggunakan
istilah kuno semacam itu.</font>

422
00:29:26,476 --> 00:29:28,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada kata yang lebih bagus.</font>

423
00:29:30,145 --> 00:29:31,276
<font color=#FFFF00>Rekan.</font>

424
00:29:37,855 --> 00:29:41,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, sakit. Lepaskan sekarang.</font>

425
00:29:41,625 --> 00:29:44,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak punya kuncinya.
Kuncinya di kantor polisi.</font>

426
00:29:46,795 --> 00:29:49,526
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti bercanda./
Tidak ada. Aku serius.</font>

427
00:29:50,966 --> 00:29:52,036
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah gila?</font>

428
00:29:52,036 --> 00:29:54,506
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, kau pasti menyuruhku menyetir.</font>

429
00:29:55,405 --> 00:29:58,135
<font color=#FFFF00>Kelihatannya cocok./ Kelihatannya...</font>

430
00:29:58,335 --> 00:30:01,545
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, tidak ada yang berubah
walau aku kembali ke tubuhku.</font>

431
00:30:01,545 --> 00:30:04,176
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, ayo./ Kemana?</font>

432
00:30:04,176 --> 00:30:06,216
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo./ Kenapa tiba-tiba lari?</font>

433
00:30:06,216 --> 00:30:08,385
<font color=#FFFF00>1, 2, 3.</font>

434
00:30:10,186 --> 00:30:11,315
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sangat cepat.</font>

435
00:30:11,655 --> 00:30:13,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Cha Dong Tak!</font>

436
00:30:13,609 --> 00:30:55,309
